1. *Bogovi* su se smejali dok su posmatrali čovekovu ludost. (The *gods* were laughing while watching human folly.)
2. Čovek veruje u postojanje *bogova*. (Man believes in the existence of *gods*.)
3. Možda *bogovi* čuju naše molitve. (Maybe *gods* hear our prayers.)
4. Neki ljudi se boje *bogova*. (Some people are afraid of *gods*.)
5. *Bogovi* daju život zemlji. (The *gods* give life to the earth.)
6. Sve se može rešiti ako se pomolimo *bogovima*. (Everything can be solved if we pray to *gods*.)
7. Veruje se da *bogovi* pomažu dobrotvornim ljudima. (It is believed that *gods* help charitable people.)
8. *Bogovi* iz stare mitologije su veoma interesantni. (The *gods* from ancient mythology are very interesting.)
9. Neki ljudi se mole više *bogovima* u različitim religijama. (Some people pray to more *gods* in different religions.)
10. Svi se nadaju da će *bogovi* biti na njihovoj strani. (Everyone hopes that the *gods* will be on their side.)